            <title type="text">《对马岛之鬼》白金后简评</title>
            <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://aozaki-kuro.com/posts/2020-08-04-ghost-of-tsushima/ghost-of-tsushima/" />
            <id>https://aozaki-kuro.com/posts/2020-08-04-ghost-of-tsushima/ghost-of-tsushima/</id>
            <updated>2020-08-05T14:18:53&#43;08:00</updated>
            <published>2020-08-04T20:51:02&#43;08:00</published>
            <author>
